{"tid":689893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[redvelvet]頭先比wendy見到我睇住youtube玩jer仔....18+","createTime":"2018-06-04T12:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T16:22:30.000Z","uid":52073,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"74e4266df7f9920a5fa716513ddca6121128abd0","tid":689893,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"頭先係屋企無聊冇野做就想玩下jer仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就緊係開youtube睇下fancam 玩下jer咁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知wendy冇啦啦開我門走入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   (因為戴緊耳機聽唔到開門聲)<br />\n我即刻呆左...仲比佢見到我全祼玩jer.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然已經同佢玉帛相見過,不過係呢個moment真係尷尬到唔想做人....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我打破沉默講左句what happend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢都仲未比我反應我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後我就去關番道門繼續玩jer仔了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一陣仲要同佢食飯...唔知點面對佢了....好尷尬..."},{"pid":"a522e6200233304d3cdc1455bd90512ef1a2b3c9","tid":689893,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"頭先玩jer仔果條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yCEsf-C7mFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyCEsf-C7mFk&d=kfJ6dqTQSMV4LBa3TGesq2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=de8cfc61\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yCEsf-C7mFk</a>"},{"pid":"9624ec7b408681697d664365ff2f97e6b2c5c3c2","tid":689893,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/200152_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai